1.0.name: wordpress/toronto
1.0.description: A blog theme based on the city of Toronto. Featuring two columns, a fixed-width, and a custom header - this wordpress template has been tastefully and skillfully designed to reflect the sleek and refined milieu of our city. Designed and developed by 9th sphere in Toronto.
